@startuml Program_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: Bug Bounty Program Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Bug Bounty Program State Transitions

[*] --> Draft : Organization creates program

Draft --> Review : Submit for review
Draft --> [*] : Delete draft

Review --> Active : Admin approves
Review --> Draft : Requires changes

Active --> Paused : Temporarily suspend
Active --> Closed : End program

Paused --> Active : Resume program
Paused --> Closed : End program

Closed --> Archived : Archive after 90 days
Archived --> [*]

note right of Draft
  Program setup:
  - Scope definition
  - Reward tiers
  - Rules & policies
end note

note right of Active
  Accepting reports:
  - Researchers can submit
  - Visible in listings
  - Notifications enabled
end note

note right of Paused
  Temporarily inactive:
  - No new submissions
  - Existing reports continue
  - Can be resumed
end note

note right of Closed
  Program ended:
  - No new submissions
  - Final reports processed
  - Statistics finalized
end note

@enduml